Sattamaṁ. 
Sūriyapeyyālaṁ. 
Tassuddānaṁ 
Kalyāṇamittaṁ sīlañca, 
chando ca attasampadā; 
Diṭṭhi ca appamādo ca, 
yoniso bhavati sattamaṁ. 
