Dhamme …pe… 
saṅghe …pe… 
yaṁ kho pana kiñci kule deyyadhammaṁ sabbaṁ taṁ appaṭivibhattaṁ sīlavantehi kalyāṇadhammehī”ti. 
“Lābhā te, godhe, suladdhaṁ te, godhe. 
