‘Idaṁ dukkhanirodhaṁ ariyasacca’nti me, bhikkhave, pubbe ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṁ udapādi, ñāṇaṁ udapādi, paññā udapādi, vijjā udapādi, āloko udapādi. 
‘Taṁ kho panidaṁ dukkhanirodhaṁ ariyasaccaṁ sacchikātabba’nti me, bhikkhave, pubbe …pe… udapādi. 
